There was one other sighting in Chicago on or around September 28th 2012
divs: sighting detailsi was up late thursday night\friday morning after a long night of socializing i was unable to unwind and fall asleep. i'm a professional photographer and always have a camera handy. for reasons i don't understand i was compelled to go outside of my building on the street around 5am and take wide angle photos of the immediate neighborhood. i took about 20 frames then returned to my apartment and fell asleep and did not notice anything unusual. upon reviewing the the images later in the day i noticed what appeared to be objects in formation glowing and hovering in the sky. i'll attach a hi-res image. i ask that you do not publish my photo without permission where as copyright is pending for the image.
Summary: objects showed up in photos. i was unaware of the event until reviewing the photos.
